msgid ""
"<1.so>Hmm...<2.pa> Ah, these <3.se_co>two tiny stone statues<4.re_co>\n"
"depicted here...<5.pa>and that faint view of the\n"
"<6.se_co>Bridge of Hylia<7.re_co> in the distance...\n"
"<8.so>From this angle, <9.pa>I think perhaps this is\n"
"the northeast shore of <10.se_co>Lake Hylia<11.re_co>.\n"
"\n"
"Possibly <12.se_co>Scout's Hill<13.re_co> or perhaps a\n"
"little further east of there."
msgstr ""

