msgid ""
"<1.so>That's all I know, I'm afraid...<2.pa>\n"
"Sorry, but you'll have to follow your\n"
"own feet if you want to find it.\n"
"But these statues...<3.pa> They look like a\n"
"husband and wife embracing. Such a\n"
"simple yet charming sight."
msgstr ""

